{"title":"严细成风高质量","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"严细成风高质量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单人独马自觉严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集中作战讲质量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分散施工不变样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单人独马自觉严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导不在不转向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严可以出战斗力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严可以出高标准；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要求严可以做到细，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细也就是严的体现；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严和细就是革命精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和科学精神具体的结合。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心保质量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶风冒雨建炼厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心保质量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严在每个毫米上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细在每个丝扣上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过得硬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁可要一个当当响的“过得硬”，也不要九十九个“过得去”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想和螺丝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想松一分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螺丝松一扣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想松了劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螺丝掉下来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百年大计"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活不能满足于当时不出问题，要想到它几十年、几百年能不能保险。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}